        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>计算几何的本质就是背板 ——卢爷</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>特此鸣谢为我们讲课/布置作业的LJZ学长</strong></p>
<h1 id="基础技能">基础技能</h1>
<h2 id="叉积和点积">叉积和点积</h2>
<img src="https://gvz-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/20200302165551.jpg" style="zoom:33%;" />
<img src="https://gvz-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/20200302165552.jpg" style="zoom:33%;" />
<p>这里是向量运算模块的代码：</p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">struct Point {
	double x, y;
	Point(double x=0,double y=0){}
	friend Point operator + (const Point &amp;a, const Point &amp;b) {return Point(a.x + b.x, a.y + b.y);}
	friend Point operator - (const Point &amp;a, const Point &amp;b) {return Point(a.x - b.x, a.y - b.y);}
	friend Point operator * (const Point &amp;a, const double &amp;b) {return Point(a.x * b, a.y * b);}
	double norm() {return sqr(x) + sqr(y);}
} p[maxn];
double det(Point a, Point b) {
    return a.x * b.y - a.y * b.x;
}
double dot(Point a, Point b) {
    return a.x * b.x + a.y * b.y;
}
</code></pre>
<h2 id="求两条直线交点">求两条直线交点</h2>
<img src="https://gvz-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/20200302193129.jpg" style="zoom:33%;" />
<img src="https://gvz-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/20200302193143.png" style="zoom: 67%;" />
